creator: Crestech, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
● Simple Multi-Cryptocurrency ‘My Wallet’
- Mobile wallet that supports Ethereum (ETH), Bitcoin (BTC), EOS (EOS), Raven (RVN), ERC20 and EOS-based tokens.
- Additional wallets can be created with one-click. You can access transaction details for each coin/token.

● One-Time Backup of All Coins and Tokens
- Only one mnemonic or QR code+password from HD Wallet structure to manage your wallet.
- You can restore all of your coins/tokens at once!

● ERC20 & EOS Tokens Auto Discovery & Search
- The token is automatically registered when deposit is made to the card without having to add the token information.
- You can search for a specific token with the token name or contract address and show/hide each token.

● Automatic Calculation of Appropriate Network Fee
- Gas fee is automatically calculated and shown based on the blockchain network status, and there is no service charge.
- You can transfer the money manually, either quickly or slowly, depending on the transaction speed you want.

● Coin/Token Information at a Glance
- Conveniently check the market price, market capitalization, trading volume, supply, etc. on the information page.

● World's First Hybrid Cryptocurrency Wallet
- Hardware security device ‘CoinUs Keeper’ provides portability, convenience and security.
- Protect your assets safely with an optional security device 'CoinUs Keeper'.


○ App permissions
Microphone: Keeper Communication
Storage: Recover QR Code
Camera: Scan QR Code
* App permissions are not required to use the service.

descriptionHtml:
* World’s First Virtual Asset Wallet Lost Protection Service, BlockSafe Launch

* Meet BlockSafe for 9,900 won per month!
- Fail to restore wallet, up to $100k Guaranteed
- Easily restore your wallet without a private key through user verification
- Email verification to strengthen wallet security
- Email/app notification when restoring wallet
- Provides device access details

* Manage multiple wallets with one click!
- Supports BTC, ETH, ERC20, FIL, RVN, Asset
- Can create up to 10 wallets per coin
- ERC20 auto discovery & search feature
- Provides pending transaction details and app notification for all coins
- Automatic calculation for optimal network fee

* Provides DEX aggregator BlockSwap
- 700 + Tokens at the best price from various DEXs at Once
- Provides optimized price and network fee

* Supports WalletConnect for DEFI/DEX
- Easily use DEFI/DEX services like Uniswap through CoinUs app

* Acquired ISMS certification for safe service operation.
- Scope of Certification: Virtual Asset Decentralized Wallet
- Period of Validity : 2021.09.08 ~ 2024.09.07
